snippet.title: Subtitled and annotated: BS The Legend of Zelda Map 1 Episode 1 (Original Broadcast)
snippet.description:
Needed to get some Satellaview up~ Go to the BS Zelda homepage if you're interested in playing this!
http://bszelda.zeldalegends.net/

So, not many people around fansubbing videogames, are there?

Leave it to me to do something a bit on the weird side.

Anyone who can help and contribute to this would be greatly appreciated.

Episodes 2, 3 and 4 should be coming in the next few days.
